cars.description: The Chevrolet Camaro is a classic American muscle car that has been in production since 1966, initially introduced to compete with the Ford Mustang. It has gone through multiple generations, with its iconic design evolving over the years, while still retaining its performance-focused spirit.

Overview: Redesigned for 2018, the Camry offers a sportier look with enhanced performance. Engines: Available with a 2.5L 4-cylinder or a 3.5L V6 engine.Features: Advanced safety tech like Toyota Safety Sense (TSS-P), which includes adaptive cruise control, lane departure alert, and automatic high beams.
